{
  "text": "Risk assessment -this process identifies the potential threats; matches assets to the potential threats; assesses the level of risk to an asset and the impact of the threat if it was successful; correlates the vulnerability (level of risk of a threat to an asset); and assigns control measures to each threat/asset combination [CITATION_1] ; and",
